<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v7" title="Q30_v7" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>La fórmula de Euler establece que, para cierto tipo de poliedros, se cumple la relación <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, donde C es la cantidad de caras, A es la cantidad de aristas y V es la cantidad de vértices del poliedro.</p>
    <p>Un poliedro que cumple esta fórmula tiene 12 caras y 8 vértices. ¿Cuántas aristas debe tener ese poliedro para que se cumpla la relación de Euler?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">16<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si A = 16, entonces A + 2 = 16 + 2 = 18. Pero C + V = 12 + 8 = 20. Como 18 ≠ 20, esta opción no cumple la relación de Euler.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">18<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si C = 12 y V = 8, entonces C + V = 12 + 8 = 20. Para que se cumpla la fórmula, debe ocurrir que A + 2 = 20, por lo tanto A = 18. Además, 18 + 2 = 20, así que la relación se cumple exactamente.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">20<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si A = 20, entonces A + 2 = 20 + 2 = 22. Pero C + V = 12 + 8 = 20. Como 22 ≠ 20, esta opción no satisface la relación de Euler.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">22<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si A = 22, entonces A + 2 = 22 + 2 = 24. Pero C + V = 12 + 8 = 20. Como 24 ≠ 20, esta opción no cumple la relación dada.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la fórmula de Euler</strong></p>
            <p>La relación dada es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar los datos del problema</strong></p>
            <p>El poliedro tiene 12 caras y 8 vértices, es decir:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Sumar el lado izquierdo</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>La ecuación queda:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar la cantidad de aristas</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 2 en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>18</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Verificar el resultado</strong></p>
            <p>Si el poliedro tiene 18 aristas, entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>A</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>18</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Y también:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Ambos lados son iguales, por lo tanto el valor es correcto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El poliedro debe tener <strong>18 aristas</strong>. La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>